<item>
            <title>[TINKERPOP-1670] End type lost when using promise()</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/TINKERPOP-1670</link>
                <project id="12316520" key="TINKERPOP">TinkerPop</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The &lt;tt&gt;Traversal.promise&lt;/tt&gt; method loses type information when used so the type of the returned future is not as complete as it could be.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For example:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;g.V().hasLabel(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;person&quot;&lt;/span&gt;).has(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;name&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;marko&quot;&lt;/span&gt;).promise(Traversal::next);
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Returns a &lt;tt&gt;CompletableFuture&amp;lt;Object&amp;gt;&lt;/tt&gt; instead of &lt;tt&gt;CompletableFuture&amp;lt;Vertex&amp;gt;&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;g.V().hasLabel(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;person&quot;&lt;/span&gt;).promise(Traversal::toList);
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Returns a &lt;tt&gt;CompletableFuture&amp;lt;List&amp;gt;&lt;/tt&gt; instead of &lt;tt&gt;CompletableFuture&amp;lt;List&amp;lt;Vertex&amp;gt;&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The fix for this could be as simple as adding the start and end (S,E) types to the traversal that is the input of the function:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;default&lt;/span&gt; &amp;lt;T&amp;gt; CompletableFuture&amp;lt;T&amp;gt; promise(&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;final&lt;/span&gt; Function&amp;lt;Traversal, T&amp;gt; traversalFunction)
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;to:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;default&lt;/span&gt; &amp;lt;T&amp;gt; CompletableFuture&amp;lt;T&amp;gt; promise(&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;final&lt;/span&gt; Function&amp;lt;Traversal&amp;lt;S,E&amp;gt;, T&amp;gt; traversalFunction)
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Need to test this a bit more though, but I think that should work.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
